# Fleet dashboard secrets/state — never committed. HubConfig.json holds the
# enrollment secret (repo is PUBLIC); hub-credential.json is the per-machine
# credential issued back on registration. See WatcherBrain/HubConfig.example.json.
WatcherBrain/HubConfig.json
WatcherBrain/hub-credential.json
# Transient plaintext master code (written at repo root by AskIdentity.ps1,
# scrubbed by the installer after enroll) and the per-machine salted uninstall
# hash (in WatcherBrain). Bare names so they match wherever they land. Neither
# must ever be committed.
master-code.plain
uninstall-code.hash
WatcherBrain/unplugged.flag
WatcherBrain/whitelist-version.txt
WatcherBrain/poll-log-cursor.txt
# Per-machine chosen proxy port (written at install by proxy-port.js select).
WatcherBrain/proxy-port.txt
WatcherBrain/update.log
WatcherBrain/_backup_*/
